# Force LF line endings on checkout regardless of the host's
# core.autocrlf setting. Prettier/eslint enforce LF; without this,
# Windows checkouts arrive as CRLF and `prettier --check` reports
# every line as "Delete `␍`". Server CI is Linux-only today, but
# this keeps Windows dev environments working too and stays in step
# with the signalk-tailscale plugin repo.
* text=auto eol=lf
